
-----------------------------------------
- API
-----------------------------------------
   extension_start

   encoders_configure ?
   servise_configure [manual / auto]
   
   stream_start
   stream_stop
   
   extension_stop
-----------------------------------------

.

-----------------------------------------
- Launch sequence / Entities
-----------------------------------------
   obs_context: initialize, reset a/v
   --------------------------------------
   scene: wot scene only
   --------------------------------------
   source: audio source, video source
   --------------------------------------
   sceneitem: for any exclude audio
   --------------------------------------
   encoder: audio, video
   --------------------------------------
   service: youtube / twitch etc.
   --------------------------------------
   output: stream output only
-----------------------------------------

.

-----------------------------------------
- Dependencies
-----------------------------------------
   scene -> sceneitem <- video source
   --------------------------------------
   video -> encoder <- audio
   --------------------------------------
   encoder settings -> encoder
   --------------------------------------
   a/v encoders -> output -> service
-----------------------------------------

.

-----------------------------------------
- States: Loading, Ready, Started
-----------------------------------------

.

